# Bō Luó Cì Kingdom

}}
Bō Luó Cì Kingdom () was an ancient kingdom mentioned in the Chinese leishu, Cefu Yuangui, compiled during the Song dynasty (960–1279 CE). It bordered on the east of Chi Tu. However, no further information about the Bō Luó Cì Kingdom has been found, and its identification is currently uncertain.
